For RELEASE 3.7 you need to push changes to the git.bioconductor.org 
repository RELEASE_3_7 branch with a version bump to 1.0.1. See

 
http://bioconductor.org/developers/how-to/git/maintain-bioc-only/#optional-merge-changes-to-the-current-release-branch

remember that changes to the release branch should be 'bug fixes', not 
new features.

Martin

